# Where do I live?

A variable only exists **inside the curly braces `{}`** where it was created. This is called its **Scope**.

```dart
void main() {
  int score = 10; // I exist everywhere inside main!
  if (score > 5) {
    int bonus = 2; // I ONLY exist inside this if-block!
  }
  print(bonus); // ERROR! 'bonus' doesn't exist here!
}
```

